efore 1 January 2023","Unknown Error. Upload failed.":"Unknown error. Upload failed.","Unknown Error: Please try again.":"Unknown error: Please try again.","Up to {maxUploads} GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, JPGs":"Up to {maxUploads} GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, JPGs","Upload":"Upload","Upload GIFs and you’ll get notifications when people share or favorite them":"Upload GIFs and you’ll get notifications when people share or favourite them","Upload GIFs, and you’ll get notifications when people share or favorite them":"Upload GIFs, and you’ll get notifications when people share or favourite them","Upload Icon":"Upload icon","Upload To Tenor":"Upload to Tenor","Upload and Create":"Upload and create","Upload and edit your GIFs, stickers, or short MP4s to your Tenor profile to share with friends and family":"Upload and edit your GIFs, stickers or short MP4s to your Tenor profile to share with friends and family","Upload animated GIFs to Tenor to share on social media channels, text messages, and everywhere else.":"Upload animated GIFs to Tenor to share on social media channels, text messages and everywhere else.","Upload icon":"Upload icon","Upload your favorite GIFs!":"Upload your favourite GIFs!","Upload your own GIFs":"Upload your own GIFs","Uploader":"Uploader","Uploading...":"Uploading…","Urdu":"Urdu","Use of Tenor on LG is subject to the {link}":"Use of Tenor on LG is subject to the {link}","Username":"Username","Uzbek":"Uzbek","Vietnamese":"Vietnamese","View Favorites":"View Favourites","View Uploads":"View uploads","Visual Expression":"Visual expression","We could not find the page you were looking for.":"We could not find the page that you were looking for.","We've updated our {linkElements}. By continuing you agree to Tenor's {linkElements}.":"We've updated our {linkElements}. By continuing, you agree to Tenor's {linkElements}.","Website Licenses":"Website licences","Welcome back!":"Welcome back!","Why Become a Content Partner?":"Why become a content partner?","Width":"Width","With Tenor, maker of GIF Keyboard, add popular {titleFragment} animated GIFs to your conversations. Share the best GIFs now \u003E\u003E\u003E":"With Tenor, maker of GIF keyboard, add popular {titleFragment} animated GIFs to your conversations. Share the best GIFs now \u003E\u003E\u003E","Work with the Tenor team to curate and optimize your library based on performance insights.":"Work with the Tenor team to curate and optimise your library based on performance insights.","X axis":"X-axis","Y axis":"Y-axis","Yes":"Yes","Yesterday":"Yesterday","You do not have access to this page.":"You do not have access to this page.","You have selected {lang}":"You have selected {lang}","Your session has expired. Please log in.":"Your session has expired. Please log in.","Zulu":"Zulu","failed to load gif frames":"failed to load GIF frames","flag icon":"flag icon","here":"here","to upload to Tenor":"to upload to Tenor","trash icon":"Bin icon","unsupported data type {mediaType}":"unsupported data type {mediaType}","upload your media files by dropping them here":"upload your media files by dropping them here","view profile":"view profile","{countStr} share":"{countStr} share","{countStr} shares":"{countStr} shares","{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since it is not a GIF, MP4, PNG or JPEG":"{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since it is not a GIF, MP4, PNG or JPEG","{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since they are not GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, or JPEGs":"{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since they are not GIFs, MP4s, PNGs or JPEGs","{gifKeyboardLogo} for iMessage":"{gifKeyboardLogo} for iMessage","{h1_title} - {first3Terms} - Discover & Share GIFs":"{h1_title} – {first3Terms} – discover and share GIFs","{name} icon":"{name} icon","{statusCode} Error":"{statusCode} error","{titleFragment} GIF Pack":"{titleFragment} GIF pack","{titleFragment} GIFs":"{titleFragment} GIFs","{titleFragment} GIFs | Tenor":"{titleFragment} GIFs | Tenor","{trimmedTime}\u002F{trimmedLength} seconds":"{trimmedTime}\u002F{trimmedLength} seconds","{username} hasn’t uploaded any GIFs!":"{username} hasn’t uploaded any GIFs!","{username}'s GIFs on Tenor":"{username}'s GIFs on Tenor"},"url path component":{"about-faq":"about-faq","about-us":"about-us","collections":"collections","contact":"contact","contentpartners":"contentpartners","emotional-graph":"emotional-graph","explore":"explore","gif-maker":"gif-maker","imessage":"imessage","legacy-account-recover":"legacy-account-recover","legal-privacy":"legal-privacy","legal-privacy-update":"legal-privacy-update","legal-terms":"legal-terms","legal-terms-developer-update":"legal-terms-developer-update","legal-terms-update":"legal-terms-update","legal\u002Fdata-usage":"legal\u002Fdata-usage","legal\u002Fprivacy":"legal\u002Fprivacy","official":"official","packs":"packs","partners":"partners","reactions":"reactions","search":"search","users":"users","view":"view"}},"tos":"\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Ca id=\"_folro4uvmxoj\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003ELast updated: 3 March 2021\u003C\u002Fh3\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETenor includes the Tenor mobile app, Tenor’s website (located at http:\u002F\u002Ftenor.com), the Tenor extensions and the Tenor API. The Tenor API may be integrated with third-party devices or services, but any Tenor-related services are provided by Google.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo use Tenor, you must accept (1) the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms?hl=en\"\u003EGoogle Terms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and (2) these Tenor Additional Terms of Service (the '\u003Cstrong\u003ETenor Additional Terms\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E').\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPlease read each of these documents carefully. Together, these documents are known as the '\u003Cstrong\u003ETerms\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E'. They establish what you can expect from us as you use our services, and what we expect from you.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf these Tenor Additional Terms conflict with the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms?hl=en\"\u003EGoogle Terms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, these Additional Terms will govern for Tenor.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlthough it’s not a part of these Terms, we encourage you to read our \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fprivacy?hl=en\"\u003EPrivacy Policy\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to better understand how you can \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Faccount.google.com\u002F\"\u003Eupdate, manage, export and delete your information\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E1. Your content.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETenor allows you to submit, store, send, receive or share your content. Your content is licensed to Google as described in the Google Terms of Service – so if you upload content to Tenor, we may display that content to users and share it when directed, and those users (including users who access content through the Tenor API) may view, share and modify that content.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2. Prohibited content.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.1 You must not use Tenor for any commercial purpose or for the benefit of any third party.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.2 As we explain in the Google Terms of Service, we want to maintain a respectful environment for everyone. When using Tenor, you must follow our \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Ftenor\"\u003EProgramme policies\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and the basic rules of conduct described in the Google Terms of Services. In particular, when using Tenor, you must not:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ea. submit, store, send or share any content that:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ei. violates, or encourages any conduct that would violate, applicable law or others' rights, including any content that infringes, misappropriates or violates someone else's intellectual property rights, or rights of publicity or privacy;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eii. contains personal or contact information about any other person without their prior authorisation;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eiii. promotes illegal or harmful activities or substances;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eiv. is fraudulent, misleading or deceptive;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ev. is false or defamatory;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Evi. is obscene or pornographic;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Evii. promotes or constitutes discrimination, bigotry, racism, hatred, harassment or harm against any individual or group;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eviii. is violent or threatening or promotes violence or actions that are threatening to any individual, group or organisation; or\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eb. send any unsolicited or unauthorised advertising, promotional materials or communications, including email, mail, spam, chain letters or other solicitations.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.3 Any content assessed as inappropriate, illegal or incompatible may be restricted or removed. We use a combination of systems to identify and assess content generated by or uploaded into our services that violates our policies, such as these terms, Google \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms\"\u003ETerms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, or that violates the law. However, we understand that we sometimes make mistakes. If you think that your content doesn't violate these terms or was removed in error, you can appeal.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou may be restricted from using our service, or have your account suspended or terminated if:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eyou materially or repeatedly breach these terms;\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ewe're required to do so to comply with a legal requirement or a court order;\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ewe reasonably believe that your conduct causes harm or liability to a user, a third-party or Tenor – for example, by hacking, phishing, harassing, spamming, misleading others or scraping content that doesn't belong to you or you have submitted, stored, shared or sent any prohibited content.\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003C\u002Ful\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor more information about why we disable accounts and what happens when we do, see this Help Centre \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Faccounts\u002Fanswer\u002F40695?sjid=7465486218302094232-NA\"\u003Earticle\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. If you believe that your Tenor Account has been suspended or terminated in error, you can \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Faccounts\u002Fanswer\u002F40695?sjid=7465486218302094232-NA\"\u003Eappeal\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E"}</script></body></html>